/- ----- Z20000  (Q182505)  [representation_mismatch] ----- -/
/-- Wikifunctions Z20000 "Bayes' theorem conditional probability P(A|B)" вЂ” Wikidata Q182505.
    Inputs (в„љ): likelihood P(B|A) = `pBA`, prior P(A) = `pA`, evidence P(B) = `pB`.
    Returns the posterior P(A|B) = P(B|A)В·P(A)/P(B).

