    (Mathlib.Probability.ConditionalProbability) states the abstract measure-theoretic
    form `Ој[t | s] = (Ој s)вЃ»В№ * Ој[s | t] * Ој t` over в„ќв‰Ґ0в€ћ, which is noncomputable.
    This spec is the faithful computable в„љ-arithmetic oracle mirroring that identity
    with `Ој s в†¦ pB`, `Ој[s | t] в†¦ pBA`, `Ој t в†¦ pA`. -/
